maven清除下载失败的jar
```
@echo off  
rem create by sunhao(sunhao.java@gmail.com)  
rem crazy coder  
    
rem -- 这里写你的仓库路径  
set REPOSITORY_PATH=C:\Users\Administrator\.m2\repository
rem -- 正在搜索...  
for /f "delims=" %%i in ('dir /b /s "%REPOSITORY_PATH%\*lastUpdated*"') do (  
    del /s /q %%i  
)  
rem 搜索完毕  
pause
```
